@node section6 "Other doors by Ian Chapman"

                      @{b}Other Doors by Ian Chapman@{ub}

RemoteRAWDL - Allows users to RAW download any file off your BBS without you
              needing to be involved! So if you are abscent and they need
              a file they can type in the pathname and DL it. Only
              reccomended to give Co-Sysops access to this door.
              MAXs BBS only.

Timegen - Run it on logon on and a user had a 5:1 chance of winning, should
          they do so then they are randomly credited with an amount of time      
          ranging from 1-60 mins. Just a bit of fun!
          MAXs and Paragon BBSs!


Amiquote - The best message to next caller door for MAXs and it's also
           Paragon compatible! Features up to 15 lines and 70 chars, the
           user may save their message a any time! The user has a choice 
           of colours in which to display their message, including a
           random colour option! They get to choose an adverb which makes
           the sent by line more interesting! for the sysop it logs the
           time, date and name of any user that uses it and it detects
           % sybols and commas and swearing!

NewFileCheck - Allows users to search for new files since their last call or 
               a specific date when they logon! Sysop configurable ANSI screen
               aswell!

@endnode

