@endnode

@node section5 "Using the door"

                        @{b}Using the door@{ub}

When the door is run a requestor will pop up on the workbench screen,
selecr the file you main then select ok, you will be given the choice to
continue with the download. Then once this is finished you'll be given the
option of performing another download.

@endnode
